Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's energy bill
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407j95
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 14 Aug 1977
Carter's energy bill, aimed at reducing oil dependence, passed by Congress. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.